Avoid this unsafe pattern from `ArgsManager` and `CWallet`:

```cpp
class A
{
    Mutex mutex;
    Foo member GUARDED_BY(mutex);
    const Foo& Get()
    {
        LOCK(mutex);
        return member;
    } // callers of `Get()` will have access to `member` without owning the mutex.
```
